HEADWORD: Agrarianism
<hw>A*gra"ri*an*ism</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An equal or
equitable division of landed property; the principles or acts of those
who favor a redistribution of land.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

